==Description==

The [[File:Spreadsheet_StyleUnderline.svg|24px]] '''Spreadsheet StyleUnderline''' tool toggles the contents of selected cells to/from underlined.

==Usage==

# Make sure there is an active [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|spreadsheet]].
# Select one or more cells.
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_StyleUnderline.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_StyleUnderline|Underline Text]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Spreadsheet → Styles → [[File:Spreadsheet_StyleUnderline.svg|16px]] Underline Text}} option from the menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Ctrl}}+{{KEY|U}}. {{Version|1.1}}


